description:
Non-material amendment to planning permission ref: P2019/3481/FUL, dated 08/12/2020. The applicant seeks to amend Condition 2 (Approved Plans) to allow for:
- Minor changes to fenestration and detailing on all elevations; 
- Minor internal reconfiguration works; 
- Minor adjustment to the pitched roof of the Canal Building; 
- The addition of an abseil rail to front of existing roof eave on the canal side elevation; 
- The redistribution of the approved solar PV panels and relocation of 18 panels to the southern roof of Thorley Works, and; 
- The addition of two access hatches in the roof (above the cores) and the repositioning of the low-level rooflights.
